{"tid":1352943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［已破解］面對白色恐怖，最佳解決方法","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T05:06:14.000Z","uid":41458,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1816c944c01bfc4500cb74145934666542a8cb6","tid":1352943,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:01:30.000Z","msg":"今次明顯係有意散播白色恐怖 <br />\n特登畀你睇警黑合作<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最好嘅方法係面對佢<br />\n大家要若無其事如常出街</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好淆底著白衫，呢D 懦夫示弱嘅行為</span></span><br />\n如果有人傳邊度有黑社會打人<br />\n首先唔好亂咁傳錄音，假影片（記返當年盲搶鹽疫埠事件），甚至<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小心連登上嘅post, 連登已被大量滲透帶風</span></span>向<br />\n大家要做嘅唔係逃避<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家帶裝備一齊出嚟守護，我地先係呢個城市嘅大多數</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要畏懼白色恐怖 大家一齊面對佢打沉佢</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c4d603b72e777fbae1b4f4b7b2e6d85d52cc3a5","tid":1352943,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇其他意見？"},{"pid":"eaab80b254d62fe52b159c4530e3479ce0bab2bb","tid":1352943,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d364817e84bbb6110208c2b0392b9991f86a5d61","tid":1352943,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4664c61abe600f95722d5873ef26aacf20a5c2b6","tid":1352943,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314efa264f0115ef9e84c8d703c20bdcf94e0030","tid":1352943,"uid":80814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"